item.title: Fall 2020 Interest Meeting
item.description: The Fall 2020 interest meeting will be held on Nov 22nd, 2020 from 1:00PM to 1:30PM ET. Here is the zoom link (please sign in with your yale.edu email): yale.zoom.us/j/97147651577 Please fill out this membership interest form (https://forms.gle/X2k8scLqNkgsvLv1A) to join the Yale Undergrad Quantum Computing group mailing list and more. Slides and more information will be added after the interest meeting!
